track_notes: Great walk which takes in the Wainwright Outlying Fells of Brock Barrow, Low Light Haw and High Light Haw to reach Top o Selside. You could follow the permissive track through Grass Holme back. There is no parking in High Nibthwaite.
track_title: A route from Water Park includes Wainwright Outlyers

track_notes:
The car park is off the road and cannot be seen from the road. It is marked on the OS map but there are no signs on the road. 

The walk starts in the wood to join the track. I used this for the UKAC so stopped at the 1st cairn in the AZ.

The split in the route is at the summit of the track, the main path is just beyond the summit of the track.
track_title: From Hidden Car Park, there and back.
